fields.name: Nike Air Max 270
fields.description: Nike's first lifestyle Air Max brings you style, comfort and big attitude in the Nike Air Max 270. The design draws inspiration from Air Max icons, showcasing Nike's greatest innovation with its large window and fresh array of colors.

fields.name: NIKE SB ZOOM BLAZER MID PRM
fields.description: The Zoom Blazer Mid is an iconic hoops shoe tailored to the needs of the modern skateboarder. Textured suede creates a premium yet durable feel, while tacky rubber adds flexible grip and comfort that lasts.

fields.name: Nike Dunk Low
fields.description: Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, the b-ball icon recalls another era with a nod to one of the original Dunk colors: University Blue. With its retro hoops design, the Dunk Low channels '80s vintage back onto the streets while its padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhereâ€”in comfort.

fields.name: Nike ACG "Cinder Cone"
fields.description: Adventure beckons. The Nike ACG Jacket answers the challenge with lightweight, water-repellent fabric that's made with 100% recycled nylon fibers. It's ready for unexpected weather on warm days, so you can easily pack it away when not in use. Subtle details nod to cinder cones, the natural result of cooled lava from Hawaii's famous volcanoes.

fields.name: Nike Club Leggings
fields.description:
Product InfoDeliveryReturns
Elevate your everyday staples with these women's Club Leggings from Nike. In an Oil Green colourway, these tight-fit leggings are made with a super-soft, lightweight cotton blend fabric. With added stretch for easy wear, they feature a high-rise elasticated waistband for a snug, secure fit. Finished up with signature Swoosh branding above the hem. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small

fields.name: Hoodrich Crescent Boyfriend T-Shirt
fields.description: Rep a roomy look with this women's Crescent Boyfriend T-Shirt from Hoodrich. In a Black colourway, this oversized top has a ribbed crew neckline, dropped shoulders and relaxed sleeves to keep it laidback. Made from soft yet durable cotton, it's finished up with contrasting Hoodrich branding to the chest, side and nape. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Converse Retro Chuck Taylor Shorts
fields.description: Add style to your summer staples with these women's Retro Chuck Taylor Shorts from Converse. In a Black colourway, these roomy shorts have a mid-rise waistband and drawcord tie for a custom fit. They're made from soft, fleecy cotton fabric for everyday comfort. Finished up with open-hand side pockets and the iconic All Star patch embroidered to the left leg. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'5" and wears a size small

fields.name: Adidas Originals Varsity Crew Sweatshirt
fields.description: Get a snug style with a vintage vibe from adidas Originals with this women's Varsity Crew Sweatshirt. Exclusive to JD, this relaxed fit sweat is made from a blended cotton recycled poly fabric for a super-soft and snug feel. It features a ribbed crewneck and stretchy ribbed trims for a classic look and an elevated fit. Finished with adidas Originals branding to the chest

fields.name: Emporio Armani EA7 Ventus Full Zip Tracksuit
fields.description: Double your heat with this premium Ventus Full Zip Tracksuit from Emporio Armani EA7. In a Grey colourway, this standard-fit suit is made with a lightweight and breathable poly fabric to keep you comfy whatever your plans. It features a hoodie that has full zip fastening with an adjustable hood for personalised coverage, elastic trims to elevate the fit and zippered pockets for storage. The matching track pants have a supportive elastic waistband, cuffed ankles so you can flex your kicks, and side pockets for quick access. Signed off with EA7 branding to the chest and thigh. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 38.5" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Jordan MVP Graphic Crew Sweatshirt
fields.description: Level up your everyday layers with this men's MVP Graphic Crew Sweatshirt from Jordan. In a Sail colourway, this regular-fit sweatshirt is made with soft brushed fleece fabric for lasting comfort. It features a classic crew neckline and long sleeves, with stretchy ribbing at the cuffs and hem to secure the fit. Finished up with a bold, oversized Jordan wordmark across the back, with Jumpman branding up front to sign off. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 40" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Champion Script Logo Core Hoodie
fields.description: Get an essential layer with this men's Script Logo Core Hoodie from Champion. Coming in a White colourway, this regular-fit hoodie is made made from a cotton poly blended fabric that's soft and breathable for cosy wear. It has a classic pullover design and features an adjustable hood for custom coverage, ribbed trims to hold the shape and a kangaroo pocket for storage. Signed off with Champion branding to the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 40" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Under Armour UA Armour Fleece Grid Full Zip Hoodie
fields.description: Grab a fresh layer with this men's UA Armour Fleece Grid Full Zip Hoodie from Under Armour. Coming in a Steel Grey colourway, this standard-fit hoodie is cut from poly fabric for lasting comfort. It features a full-length zip-up fastening with an adjustable hood for custom coverage, as well as a split kangaroo pocket for storage. It has ribbed trims to secure the fit, with durable woven panels and is finished up with classic Under Armour branding at the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 40" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Adidas Originals Trefoil Essential Fleece Hoodie
fields.description: Freshen up your laidback looks with this men's Trefoil Essential Fleece Hoodie from adidas Originals, exclusive to JD. In a Wonder Blue colourway, this regular-fit hoodie is made with a soft cotton-recycled poly fleece fabric for supreme comfort. It features an adjustable hood to amp up the coverage, and stretchy ribbed trims to secure the shape. With a kangaroo pouch up front for quick storage, it's finished with adidas Originals' iconic Trefoil to the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'1" with a 36.5" chest and wears a size medium. | IS2248

fields.name: Adidas Originals Classic Monogram Backpack
fields.description: Stash your essentials when on the move with this Classic Monogram Backpack from adidas Originals. In a Black colourway, this bag is cut from smooth recycled polyester fabric for lasting use. It features a zip-around main compartment for storage, with two front pouches for your smaller bits. It has adjustable straps for a custom fit, with a loop handle for easy carry. Finished up with monogram Trefoil branding throughout.

fields.name: New Era MLB San Diego Padres 59FIFTY Cap
fields.description: Level up your 'fit in support of your team with this MLB San Diego Padres 59FIFTY Cap from New Era. In a Walnut Brown colourway, this cap has a full, structured crown and is cut from smooth, lightweight polyester fabric for everyday comfort. It features a flat visor for coverage, with eyelets for ventilation. Finished up with the Padres crest to the front, with a patch to the side. Hand wash.

fields.name: Nike Just Do It Mini Backpack
fields.description: Stash your stuff when on the go with this juniors' Just Do It Mini Backpack from Nike. In a Medium Soft Pink colourway, this bag is cut from smooth polyester for lasting use. It features a zip-up main compartment for secure storage, with side pockets and a front pouch for added space. It has padded, adjustable straps for a comfy feel, with a loop handle for an easy carry. Finished up with the 'Just Do It' slogan and Nike Swoosh branding. Hand wash. Dimensions: 33cm H x 25cm W x 13cm

fields.name: Nike Essential Chaser Sunglasses
fields.description: Round off your look in style with these Essential Chaser Sunglasses from Nike. In a Black and Grey colourway, these glasses are made from lightweight plastic for durability. They feature tinted lenses for ray protection, with folding arms for easy storage. Finished up with Nike Swoosh branding
